import sys

def main(args):
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))

    stack = []
    for i in range(n):
        stack.append(a[i])
        stack.reverse()
        for j in range(len(stack)):
            print(stack[j], end=' ')
        print()
    return 0

if __name__ == '__main__':
    sys.exit(main(sys.argv))
